{"tid":1052282,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過有人搭緊枱的時候飛象過河夾你d餸？","createTime":"2019-03-08T07:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T08:59:18.000Z","uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"19e9e06380ad189edfdf0bb103af29267110eaa8","tid":1052282,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:55:06.000Z","msg":"話說好多年前同同事食晏，兩條友四人枱坐埋一邊，對面坐住搭枱既人。食食下飯，對面嗰個人好順手咁夾左我碟兩餸飯既一條菜，我呆左。佢繼續睇電話我就同佢講。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：先生唔好意思，你食左我條菜。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：呀!!!!!!! 係咩，係喎，唔好意思，我俾番錢你。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔駛嘞，無緊要，話你知唧，幾好食呀﹗<br />\n佢已經勁唔好意思咁笑。我同同事笑到仆街。臨走時仲抽鳩佢水。下次唔好嘞下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f62b8589ad95e377fc8f5ea726680823ff669a","tid":1052282,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:55:26.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"7c4b107c60808b604afdfa0118b119c3bb39be55","tid":1052282,"uid":53254,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.giphy.com/media/xT5P0s6cg7G7ppCQhi/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FxT5P0s6cg7G7ppCQhi%2Fgiphy.gif&h=5292b52d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}